        <h5>Tok</h5>
        <h6>October 12</h6>
        <q>ATV on frozen trails through swamp with no snow yet. These are good conditions for travel. Mud holes are frozen so ATV doesn't get stuck and no snow to plow through.</q>

        <p>This change affects hunting and fishing. I first started noticing this change in 2006, and now I observe it yearly. It has no effect on safety.</p>
