        <h6>November 3</h6>
        <q>The trapline trail with not enough snow to snowmachine on. I had to use 4x4s to set the trapline - too little snow for snow-gos, areas were limited as 4x4s can't go some places (ATVs).</q>
        <p>This change affects trapping. I first started noticing this change in 2005 and now observe it seasonally. It has a strong effect on safety.</p>
